        <p>
          Blockchain Badges enables organizations to award Web3-native digital certifications that recipients can own and verify permanently. By bridging Web2 and Web3, the platform makes it effortless to create blockchain-based badges and immediately experience the value they bring.
        </p>
        <p>
          The process is remarkably straightforward. In just a few steps, organizations can design, mint, and distribute verifiable credentials for event participation, learning rewards, or achievement unlocks. This simplicity is powered by the BWS Platform infrastructure, which ensures reliable delivery and permanent verification.
        </p>
        <p>
